'''美国外国情报监控法院'''（{{lang-en|United States Foreign Intelligence Surveillance Court}}，缩写为'''FISC'''），是根据美国1978年《{{tsl|en|Foreign Intelligence Surveillance Act|外国情报监控法}}》建立的[[联邦法院|联邦法院]]，主要任务是审查[[美國聯邦執法部門列表|联邦执法机构]]對於监控境內外國間諜和外国情报机构的请求。此类请求通常是由美国[[国家安全局|国家安全局]]和[[联邦调查局|联邦调查局]]提出。在成立后，其权力不断拓展，甚至被成为“几乎与最高法院平行的法院”。

1978年成立後至2009年，法院位於[[羅伯特·F·甘迺迪司法部大樓|羅伯特·F·甘迺迪司法部大樓]]6樓<ref name="fisc moving" /><ref name="secret-court judges upset" />，2009年後法院搬遷至[[華盛頓哥倫比亞特區|華盛頓特區]]的{{tsl|en|E. Barrett Prettyman United States Courthouse|美國E·巴雷特·普雷特曼法院}}。<ref name="fisc moving">{{cite web |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2009/03/01/AR2009030101730.html |title=Surveillance Court Quietly Moving |first=Del Quentin |last=Wilber |work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]] |date=2009-03-02 |access-date=2013-07-10 |archive-date=2014-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140301033204/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2009/03/01/AR2009030101730.html |url-status=live }}</ref><ref name="secret-court judges upset">{{cite web |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/secret-court-judges-upset-at-portrayal-of-collaboration-with-government/2013/06/29/ed73fb68-e01b-11e2-b94a-452948b95ca8_story.html |title=Secret-Court Judges Upset at Portrayal of 'Collaboration' with Government |author=[[Carol_D._Leonnig|Leonnig, Carol D.]]; Nakashima, Ellen; [[Barton_Gellman|Gellman, Barton]] |date=2013-06-29 |work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]] |access-date=2013-07-10 |archive-date=2013-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130630155900/http://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/secret-court-judges-upset-at-portrayal-of-collaboration-with-government/2013/06/29/ed73fb68-e01b-11e2-b94a-452948b95ca8_story.html |url-status=live }} "For about 30 years, the court was located on the sixth floor of the Justice Department's headquarters, down the hall from the officials who would argue in front of it. (The court moved to the District's federal courthouse in 2009.)"</ref>

